    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Lies We Tell Ourselves（我们告诉自己的谎言）</strong>是一款<strong>分章节的第一人称心理动作冒险游戏</strong>，融合了<strong>内省/恐怖元素</strong>，注重<strong>细腻的叙事</strong>和<strong>氛围</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/67611bb130c941c2998fa718072288dc.poster.avif?t=1748781147\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/67611bb130c941c2998fa718072288dc.webm?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/67611bb130c941c2998fa718072288dc.mp4?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 一种<strong>动作冒险体验</strong>，适合恐怖游戏爱好者及非恐怖游戏玩家。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 每个章节精心设计，融合了<strong>叙事</strong>、<strong>解谜</strong>、<strong>探索</strong>甚至<strong>头目战斗</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>奇异且丰富的故事情节</strong>，拥有足够的细腻度，让玩家自行构建解读和意义。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>具有挑战性但公平的解谜</strong>，需要观察、理解和一定的抽象思维来解决。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>成熟且令人不安的主题</strong>，以尊重和谨慎的方式呈现，而非单纯追求冲击效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个章节提供<strong>约2小时的游戏内容</strong>，推动主线故事的发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/dff59cc3a1792e6f08c4d1d8ca5bd10c.poster.avif?t=1748781147\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/dff59cc3a1792e6f08c4d1d8ca5bd10c.webm?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/dff59cc3a1792e6f08c4d1d8ca5bd10c.mp4?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一个关于选择与后果的超自然故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入文森特·阿诺的世界，一个在27岁生日时，因神秘存在挑战其真实本性而生活被颠覆的男人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/f82d2ade98dda62d165df3e8929b267b.poster.avif?t=1748781147\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/f82d2ade98dda62d165df3e8929b267b.webm?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/f82d2ade98dda62d165df3e8929b267b.mp4?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索文森特复杂的成人个性，这些由过去的选择塑造的个性，引导他踏上自我发现和道德模糊的超现实内省之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/b71a662986e0ab12c9c886032c7805a8.poster.avif?t=1748781147\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/b71a662986e0ab12c9c886032c7805a8.webm?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/b71a662986e0ab12c9c886032c7805a8.mp4?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开隐藏的真相，在这个发人深省的冒险中，感知与现实的界限如同我们告诉自己的谎言一样脆弱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/059dc036c0041bd6d322839f32b46546.poster.avif?t=1748781147\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/059dc036c0041bd6d322839f32b46546.webm?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/059dc036c0041bd6d322839f32b46546.mp4?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
